Quickstrike:






Quickstrike tried to lift his head, hearing KitKat's voice. She must be 
around. He tried to focus his optics, still feeling drained and weighed 
down.

"KitKat?" he mumbled lowly. He slowly lifted his chest up, trying get up. He 
looked at his arms and saw that there were black wires on them. His face 
froze, staring at them.

Where on Earth was he? His mind paniced, now realizing that he was alone. 
Stingtra wasn't with him. He looked around. There were trains of electric 
streaming around the walls of the cave. There were pulsing sounds, lights 
here and there, and markings on the ground.

He looked to the right of himself and saw of pile of scrap metal; some 
things he reconized.

"What in--" A painful surge of electric hit his body. He screamed, and his 
upper body was pulled up.
